en & Hell Party','Chi Phi is calling all angels and devils to come party like it\'s your last day on Earth! In support of Camp Kesem.',7,NULL,'Chi Phi, 32 Hereford St., Boston','2011-04-09 22:00:00',240,42.3501793222436,-71.0862421989441,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(573,'All of the Lights Party','Come ready to party at Lambda Chi Alpha. Wear white so you stick out under the blacklight on the dance floor. Enjoy snacks and refreshments.',7,NULL,'Lambda Chi Alpha, 99 Bay State Rd., Boston','2011-04-09 22:00:00',240,42.3502744708186,-71.0975396633148,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(574,'InGLOWrious Basterds','The Eighth-Annual Theta Chi Highlighter Party is presented in conjunction with brother and WMBR-renowned DJ Bass Eel. We provide the shirts and highlighters, you provide the designs. Donâ€™t miss Boston\'s most famous highlighter party of the year.',7,NULL,'Theta Chi, 528 Beacon St., Boston','2011-04-09 22:00:00',240,42.350553,-71.090956,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(575,'ALPHA EPSILON PI PRESENTS: THE HIGHLIGHTER PARTY','Take a wild journey into space with highlighters, blacklights, and a live DJ! Paint our friends, paint your friends, or paint your friends\' friends. Join the brothers of AEPi in our beautiful Boston home. Let us highlight your CPW like no one else... 5th stop on Saferide Boston West! ',7,NULL,'Alpha Epsilon Pi, 155 Bay State Rd., Boston','2011-04-09 22:00:00',240,NULL,NULL,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(576,'ZBTron','Come enjoy the last night of CPW by partying at ZBTron. Energy drinks, black lights, and all the best music will keep you dancing into the night. Call Rick for Rides (617-232-3257).',7,NULL,'Zeta Beta Tau, 58 Manchester Rd., Brookline','2011-04-09 22:00:00',240,42.348808,-71.124008,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(577,'Telephone Pictionary','Calling all hilariously terrible artists... ;)',7,NULL,'New House (W70), House 6, 5th Floor, French House Kitchen','2011-04-09 22:00:00',90,42.3549762168149,-71.1011123657227,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(578,'Telephone Pictionary','Calling all hilariously terrible artists... ;)',7,NULL,'New House (W70), House 6, 5th Floor, French House Kitchen','2011-04-09 22:00:00',90,42.3550911792172,-71.1011391878128,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(579,'Nerdy Sing-Along','It\'s hard to overstate my satisfaction with how much this event is fulfilling in creative way. If hopes and dreams are shattering apart, remember it\'s gonna be the future soon, so apply forgetful functors to the past and be still alive.',7,NULL,'Random Hall (NW61)','2011-04-09 22:17:00',60,42.362035,-71.098074,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(580,'Bobbing for French Fries','The game-show-like thing you\'ll never forget! Voted \"the most dangerous thing I\'ve probably ever done\" by the prefrosh last year (just kidding, we\'ve never actually done this before). Lab goggles and oven mitts provided. Call 615-414-6224 for a fiery good time! ',7,NULL,'TPC Systems, 253 Commonwealth Ave., Boston','2011-04-09 22:22:00',60,NULL,NULL,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(581,'Make-Your-Own Pizza','In need for some tasty, savory food, but want to still have hands-on fun? Come make your own pizza in the Next House Country Kitchen with more than enough variety in toppings!',7,NULL,'Next House (W71)','2011-04-09 22:30:00',90,42.3545480791219,-71.1021423339844,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(582,'Juggling in Enclosed Spaces','What\'s more fun than throwing brightly colored objects at people? Doing it at the same time as fifteen other people all packed into a small lounge. Come juggle with us! Don\'t know how? We\'re happy to teach you!',7,NULL,'Random Hall (NW61)','2011-04-09 22:47:00',780,42.362035,-71.098074,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(583,'â€œCoffee and Cigarettesâ€','Watch Jim Jarmusch\'s independent film \"Coffee and Cigarettes,\" while caffeinating yourself and meeting Senior House residents. Can you guess what makes Senior House unique? ',7,NULL,'Senior House (E2)','2011-04-09 23:00:00',120,42.3599867966918,-71.0868000984192,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(584,'Blacklight Party at DU','Come party with the brothers of DU and meet co-eds from the Greater Boston area. Our resident DJ, DJ Dweck, will be mixing beats all night.',7,NULL,'Delta Upsilon, 526 Beacon St., Boston','2011-04-09 23:00:00',120,42.350581,-71.09085,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(585,'Cocoa!','Join the Fourth East hall of East Campus in their nightly cocoa tradition. If you come to MIT, you could do this every night!',7,NULL,'East Campus Courtyard (between Buildings 62 and 64)','2011-04-09 23:00:00',59,42.3600185079503,-71.0883235931396,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(586,'Pants Pants Revolution','Just like Dance Dance Revolution, except that every time you win, you put on another pair of pants.',7,NULL,'Random Hall (NW61)','2011-04-09 23:17:00',60,42.362035,-71.098074,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(587,'Capture the glowey-thing',' Is it a bird? Is it a plane? No one knows...',7,NULL,'TPC Systems, 253 Commonwealth Ave., Boston','2011-04-09 23:22:00',780,NULL,NULL,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(588,'Pixar Movie Marathon','We will be showing Pixar films like â€œThe Incredibles,â€ â€œToy Story,â€ and â€œUp.â€ Meet us at Lobby 7 to catch our Big Silver Van to Epsilon Theta.',7,NULL,'Epsilon Theta, 259 St. Paul St., Brookline','2011-04-09 23:55:00',-21705355,NULL,NULL,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(589,'Late Night Snacks at Pilam','Done Partying? Need to refuel? Stop by Pi Lambda Phi for some wings and sundaes.',7,NULL,'Pi Lambda Phi, 450 Beacon St., Boston','2011-04-09 23:59:00',91,42.3516105001831,-71.0873794555664,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(590,'Steak and Shake','Itâ€™s never too late for an obscene amount of protein and sugar. Drop by Skullhouse for your last meal of the night, hot off the grill, icy cold from the blender.',7,NULL,'Phi Kappa Sigma, 530 Beacon St., Boston','2011-04-09 23:59:00',121,42.350578,-71.090941,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(591,'Game Night at Next - The Final Boss','Youâ€™ve made it through the fun and games at CPW. At last, youâ€™re at the final boss. This is it. Come have fun with Karaoke, DDR, Guitar Hero, Twister, Midnight Glowstick Tag, Late Night Courtyard Activities, or even a pillow fight. Chat with Next House and NextExec one last time before we see you again â€œNextâ€ year!',7,NULL,'Next House (W71)','2011-04-09 23:59:00',181,42.3546432210835,-71.1022925376892,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(592,'Underground Capture the Flag','What better way to familiarize with MITâ€™s layout than our legendary Underground Capture the Flag. Join us in the tunnels and corridors at midnight with hundreds of other Prefrosh. Two teams. Two Flags. One night you will never forget.',7,NULL,'Meet in Lobby 7','2011-04-09 23:59:00',241,42.3591464425085,-71.0931944847107,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(593,'Miracle Berry Feast','Everything you thought you knew about food will be turned upside-down when you enhance your tastebuds with a miracle berry. Enter a world where tabasco sauce, vinegar, and limes will become your new best friends as you cap off your CPW experience with the brothers of Theta Xi.',7,NULL,'Theta Xi, 64 Bay State Rd., Boston','2011-04-10 00:00:00',120,42.349763,-71.095896,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(594,'Midnight Munchies','After a long night, come relax and enjoy cool drinks and fried food prepared by the Brothers of Zeta Psi.',7,NULL,'Zeta Psi, 233 Mass Ave., Cambridge','2011-04-10 00:00:00',120,42.361774493913,-71.0971802473068,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(595,'Rom Com Pillow Party!','So it\'s the last night of CPW and you\'ve met some pretty sweet people. Come cuddle up next to them or hit them with a pillow! We\'ll be playing romantic comedies all night!',7,NULL,'Burton-Conner House (W51), Porter Room','2011-04-10 00:00:00',360,42.3558483401304,-71.0981726646423,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(596,'Over-9000-Watt Halogen Light','We built a light. A very bright light. We want to talk to the International Space Station with our light. Come check out our light. It wonâ€™t seem like night anymore.',7,NULL,'East Campus Courtyard (between Buildings 62 and 64)','2011-04-10 00:01:00',59,42.3603356196558,-71.0884308815002,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(597,'Analog Caffeine Party, Late Night Edition','Want to learn the art of manual coffee brewing, sample more types of tea than your bladder can handle, or just snack on cookies and caffeine in blissful ignorance?',7,NULL,'East Campus (62), Talbot Lounge','2011-04-10 00:01:00',119,42.3601294972293,-71.0883450508118,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(598,'Sweet Rave Party','Rave-An underground party in which electronic music is played, dancing occurs in a very free-form fashion. --Urban Dictionary',7,NULL,'Random Hall (NW61)','2011-04-10 00:17:00',60,42.362035,-71.098074,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(599,'The Original Midnight Buffet','Not thinking about calling it a night, were you? Drop by the Kappa Sig stoop instead for some fried food and other snacks. Or maybe some pick-up basketball or that last game of Dance Central. ',7,NULL,'Kappa Sigma, 407 Memorial Dr., Cambridge','2011-04-10 01:00:00',90,42.3561575445816,-71.0973465442657,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(600,'Sevlev Snacking','Join us at East Campus as we gorge on snacks from Seven Eleven, the glorious 24-hour source of calories that fuels our long, long nights.',7,NULL,'Meet at East Campus (62), Talbot Lounge','2011-04-10 02:00:00',60,42.3599709410565,-71.0883450508118,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(601,'After Party ','It\'s late, but you can sleep on the way home. Come grab some food, hang out or watch a movie. 3rd stop on Saferide Boston East.',7,NULL,'Phi Sigma Kappa, 487 Commonwealth Ave., Boston','2011-04-10 02:00:00',120,NULL,0,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(602,'Late Night Philosophy/Politics Discussion','Discuss philosophy, politics, and whatever else comes to mind. Drink tea, coffee, and waste the night away. Does the Repugnant Conclusion break utilitarianism? ',7,NULL,'Senior House (E2)','2011-04-10 02:00:00',240,42.3600026523231,-71.0869717597961,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(603,'The Afterparty at TDC ','Partied out or want to take a break? Come by for some snacks and unwind with the brothers. ',7,NULL,'Theta Delta Chi, 372 Memorial Dr., Cambridge','2011-04-10 02:30:00',-21705510,42.3563557517629,-71.096482872963,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(604,'Chicken and Waffles: Afterhours','Has all that partying made you hungry? Get to know students in the Black Studentsâ€™ Union (BSU) while enjoying some delicious chicken and waffles!',7,NULL,'New House (W70), House 6, 1st Floor Lounge','2011-04-10 02:30:00',120,42.3551506424462,-71.1008280515671,6,'confirmed','minority'),(605,'Sleepers Anonymous','Sleep is an addiction. There is no \'try\', only \'do\', when it comes to kicking an addiction. Come talk about it and kick it with us. ',7,NULL,'Random Hall (NW61)','2011-04-10 03:17:00',60,42.362035,-71.098074,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(606,'The Last Breakfast','Wake up in the mornin\' feelin\' like you\'re in college. Our events were pretty awesome, this you have to acknowledge. Before you leave, brush your teeth with a sugary snack, \'cuz though you\'re leavin\' right now, you\'ll be comin\' back.',7,NULL,'Burton-Conner House (W51), TV Lounge','2011-04-10 07:00:00',180,42.3558483401304,-71.0982370376587,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(607,'Breakfast at New House - Part 3','Leaving? Grab some pancakes, eggs, waffles, bacon, and a smoothie on your way out!',7,NULL,'New House (W70), Arcade','2011-04-10 08:00:00',120,42.3551506424462,-71.1005759239197,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(608,'CPW Checkout and Evaluations','Come say goodbye to your new friends in the Admissions Office, and fill out a short form to let us know what you thought of your weekend at MIT. ',7,NULL,'Student Center (W20), 2nd Floor, La Sala de Puerto Rico','2011-04-10 08:00:00',240,42.359083,-71.094761,6,'confirmed','featured parents'),(609,'Farewell Breakfast with the Sponge-Dwellers','We know that you will be sad to leave MIT, so let Simmons bid you a yummy farewell with an exquisite breakfast! After a hectic 3 days, itâ€™s also the perfect time to relax and mingle with the Sponge-dwellers!',7,NULL,'Simmons Hall (W79), Night Cafe Lounge','2011-04-10 09:00:00',120,42.3570058669297,-71.1015200614929,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(610,'Breakfast of Champions II','An epic night at Nu Delta\'s NDurance party calls for a rewarding breakfast. The brothers of Nu Delta welcome you and wish you a safe journey back home with this scrumptious meal.',7,NULL,'Nu Delta, 460 Beacon St., Boston','2011-04-10 09:00:00',120,42.351519318073,-71.087846159935,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(611,'See you in the Fall breakfast','A giant breakfast for before you go home. We will be serving pancakes, eggs, sausage, and lots of bacon.',7,NULL,'Phi Delta Theta, 97 Bay State Rd., Boston','2011-04-10 09:00:00',180,42.350334,-71.097379,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(612,'Parent\'s Brunch','Do you have last-minute questions about fraternity life at MIT? Want one last meal before heading home? Either way, drop by Skullhouse before leaving MIT.',7,NULL,'Phi Kappa Sigma, 530 Beacon St., Boston','2011-04-10 09:00:00',180,42.350578,-71.090941,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living parents'),(613,'Sunday Mass','Celebrate Sunday Mass at the MIT Chapel with the Tech Catholic Community.',7,NULL,'MIT Chapel (W15)','2011-04-10 09:30:00',60,NULL,NULL,6,'confirmed','religious'),(614,'â€œNextâ€ to Last Event - Breakfast at Next','Stop by our country kitchen one last time before you leave; so, we can wish you goodbye with some nice warm breakfast. We hope to see you again next year!',7,NULL,'Next House (W71), Country Kitchen','2011-04-10 09:30:00',120,42.3545480791219,-71.102249622345,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(615,'Breakfast of Champions','Bagel Bagel Bagel Bagel Bagel Bagel Bagel Bagel Bagel Bagel Bagel. MUFFIN! MUFFIN!',7,NULL,'Theta Delta Chi, 372 Memorial Dr., Cambridge','2011-04-10 10:00:00',-21705960,42.3563557517629,-71.096482872963,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(616,'The Final Breakfast','Celebrate your ultimate victory over CPW. Enjoy breakfast with senior haus. ',7,NULL,'Senior House (E2)','2011-04-10 10:00:00',120,42.3599867966918,-71.0868859291077,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(617,'Phi Sig Crepes','One last meal before you come again in the fall. Our crepes are sweet and savory, hopefully just like your time here. 3rd Stop Saferide Boston East.',7,NULL,'Phi Sigma Kappa, 487 Commonwealth Ave., Boston','2011-04-10 10:00:00',120,42.349264,-71.094216,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(618,'MacGregor House Tours','Take a tour through the hallowed halls of MacGregor with one of our friendly residents. Check out what a typical room looks like, and see what facilities we have to offer.',7,NULL,'MacGregor House (W61), Lobby','2011-04-10 10:00:00',120,42.355439,-71.099777,6,'confirmed','dormitory parents'),(619,'Tours of East Campus','Come get a tour of the East Campus dorm. Hopefully you won\'t get attacked by vikings. Or maybe you think that sort of thing is cool. Leaving every half hour for most of the weekend.',7,NULL,'Meet in East Campus Courtyard (between Buildings 62 and 64)','2011-04-10 10:00:00',120,42.3600026523231,-71.0883021354675,6,'confirmed','dormitory parents'),(620,'Mindless Games','We\'ve all been awake for far to long. Come make incoherent noises with us while we play games that require as much thought as you have remaining thought capacity. Meet us at Lobby 7 to catch our Big Silver Van to Epsilon Theta.',7,NULL,'Epsilon Theta, 259 St. Paul St., Brookline','2011-04-10 10:00:00',120,NULL,0,6,'confirmed','fraternity sorority living'),(621,'Line by Line','Write haiku with us / I am the saddest haboo / Purple is a shape',7,NULL,'Random Hall (NW61)','2011-04-10 10:17:00',60,42.362035,-71.098074,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(622,'Telephone Pictionary','Calling all hilariously terrible artists... ;)',7,NULL,'New House (W70), House 6, 5th Floor, French House Kitchen','2011-04-10 10:30:00',60,42.3549762168149,-71.1011552810669,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(623,'Leftover Brunch','You\'re going to college. You will eat leftovers. Try before you buy!',7,NULL,'Random Hall (NW61)','2011-04-10 10:47:00',60,42.362035,-71.098074,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(624,'Brunch','Hungry from all the free food you\'ve been getting this weekend? Fill up for one last time. You wouldn\'t want to starve on your trip home.',7,NULL,'East Campus (62), Talbot Lounge','2011-04-10 11:00:00',60,42.359992742554,-71.0885006189346,6,'confirmed','dormitory'),(625,'MIT150 Next Century Convocation','The Next Century Convocation is a formal, academic event to honor the creative achievements, enduring values, and ethic of service that have set MIT apart since its founding and that inspire our focus on inventing the future today. Community invitation at http://web.mit.edu/mit150/next-century/.',7,NULL,'Roundtrip transportation will be provided from MIT campus to Boston Convention and Exhibition Center (BCEC).  Depart from designated bus stops at Albany St. (opp. Ashdown House), Audrey St., and Hayward St.','2011-04-10 14:00:00',180,42.3587024772707,-71.0935378074646,6,'confirmed','featured parents');
